    "synopsis": "Having driven off the blood-maddened horrors that menaced their homeworld, the Blood Angels hunt the renegade who set them loose: the infamous Fabius Bile, who has stolen a sample of their primarch's sacred blood. The trail leads to Dynikas V, a death world crawling with Tyranids, where Bile has hidden his secret laboratory. Together with their fierce kin the Flesh Tearers, Rafen and his battle-brothers descend into a nightmare of alien swarms and grotesque experiments, racing to recover what was taken before Bile can unlock the secrets of Sanguinius's gene-line. What they find there is more terrible than anything they imagined.",
